  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Priyansh, the cricket and business chat with that startup founder must have been interesting. What did you take away from it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It was good. He said focus on one thing. Many startups fail because they try too many things. Some *bhari* ideas, but not actionable."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That makes sense — focusing keeps things clear. What did you think about the cricket part of the chat?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Oh, that part was fun. He compared a cricket team to a startup — everyone has a role. If someone doesn’t do their job, the whole game suffers. I liked that analogy."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Cricket and startups both need teamwork. What made that idea land for you?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe because I play cricket, I could see what he meant. Like, a batsman can’t just think about his score — he has to work with the fielders, the bowler. Startup is same — you can’t work alone. It *click* for me."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it — the *click* is when theory meets practice. Was that idea new to you, or did it confirm something you already felt?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It confirmed something I felt. I always thought good ideas matter, but now I see execution and teamwork are equally important. Maybe more."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re doing great — that’s a solid shift in thinking. What’s one thing you want to focus on in your work now?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I want to focus more on collaboration. At work, I tend to do things alone. Maybe if I work better with my team, we can move faster. Let’s try."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds like a smart plan. Working with others can really speed things up. What’s one small way you could start collaborating more this week?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe I can ask my teammate for feedback on my code before I submit it. Or pair up for a task once. It’s small, but could help. Let’s give it a shot."
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Starting small helps build the habit. What task would you pick for that first teamwork try?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe the next API integration task. It’s something I usually do alone, but I can ask my teammate to pair with me. Two heads might spot issues I miss. Let’s see how it goes."
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That’s a solid choice — API setups can be tricky. How do you feel about asking for help on it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Honestly, I feel a bit shy. I’m used to doing things alone, so asking for help feels like a risk. But I think trying it once could be good. Let’s give it a try."
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Shyness is totally normal — but it gets easier with practice. What’s one small step you can take to start the conversation with your teammate?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe I can just message him today and say, “Hey, want to pair on the next API task? I think it could help.” That’s small, but I’ll do it. Thanks, Maya. I think I’ll give it a shot."
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re doing great — small steps matter. How do you think your teammate will react to that message?"
    }
  ],
